# ZiroWork — Single Source of Truth

---

## The North Star

> ZiroWork turns music school inquiries into enrolled, paying students — without replacing the school's CRM.

This is not a dashboard company. This is not a chat tool. This is not a browser clicker.
ZiroWork is an **AI front desk and enrollment engine** for music schools.

Every decision gets judged by one question:
> Does this help ZiroWork respond faster, enroll more students, prove ROI, or earn deeper trust?

If the answer is no — cut it.

---

## Why This Works (The ALAN Proof)

Acquisition.com built ALAN — Artificial Lead Automation and Nurture — to automate the most painful part of brick-and-mortar acquisition: working leads. It hit over $1.4M/month in its first six months. Its edge was simple: it got 1.9x more leads to show than the average front desk clerk.

The lesson is not "copy ALAN." The lesson is: **lead work is the money bottleneck.** The business that works leads faster and more consistently than the school's internal team wins every time.

ZiroWork applies that to music schools. Respond fast. Work the lead. Get them enrolled. Prove it. Keep the client.

