## The Only Win That Counts

**Enrolled.** That is the metric. That is the goal. That is what gets reported.

A "trial" is not a win. A trial is a last-resort fallback offered only when the direct enrollment approach failed after the follow-up sequence. If we are offering a trial, we are 75% of the way there — but the outcome is now out of our hands.

**Never lead with "trial." Always lead with enrollment.**

Trials are tracked separately when they happen — so we know if the lead enrolled after the trial — but enrolled on the Lead record is the SSOT for whether ZiroWork succeeded.

