## The Full Chain

```
Music School (client)
  → Instrument Program (Piano | Guitar | Voice | Drums)
    → Campaign (ad funnel for that program + location)
      → Landing Page (public form the parent fills out)
        → Lead (parent who submitted)
          → SMS Conversation (AI works the lead)
            → ENROLLED ← the win
              → Client Report updated
                → School takes over
```

ZiroWork owns everything from **Lead** through **Enrolled**. Before and after is the school's domain.

