## The Primary Flow

```
Parent fills out form
  → AI texts within 60 seconds
    → Qualify: student, instrument, schedule
      → Pitch enrollment directly
        → Slot booked, payment link sent
          → Confirmation sent
            → Reminders (24hr before, day-of)
              → ENROLLED
```

---

## The Follow-Up Flow (fallback only)

If the lead does not enroll after the primary sequence:

```
No commitment after primary outreach
  → Follow-up sequence continues (days 2–N)
    → If still not enrolled → operator offers trial as entry point
      → Trial booking created (booking_type = trial, status = pending enrollment)
        → Trial happens
          → Operator records outcome: Enrolled / Lost
            → Report updated
```

Trial bookings are entered manually by the operator — not pushed by AI. Trial is a fallback close, not a default step.

