## When a Lead Comes In

Parent submits form → n8n fires webhook → ZiroWork FastAPI receives it.

```json
{
  "event_type": "new_lead_created",
  "entity_id": "<lead-uuid>",
  "location_id": "<school-location-uuid>",
  "metadata": {
    "program": "Piano",
    "parent_name": "Sarah",
    "student_name": "Jack"
  }
}
```

`location_id` tells the system which school, which slots, which scripts, which SMS number. Every lead is fully isolated to its client.

