## Agent Routing

All routing through ZIRO_ADMIN. No agent calls another directly.

```
POST /events
  → ZIRO_ADMIN routes to sub-agent
    → Sub-agent works, returns ZiroState
      → ZIRO_ADMIN validates
        → ZIRO_MESSAGING sends text (if needed)
          → OpenPhone delivers it (gated by RAVEN_SMS_ENABLED)
```

Only ZIRO_MESSAGING sends anything externally.

Every agent returns:
```json
{
  "agent_output": {},
  "status": "complete" | "failed",
  "raven_payload": { "recipient_id": "", "message_type": "", "data": {} },
  "error": ""
}
```

