## Lead to Enrolled (full step-by-step)

```
new_lead_created
  → ZIRO_LEADS scores: HOT / WARM / COLD
    → ZIRO_MESSAGING sends first text (<60 seconds)
      → Conversation runs (AI handles replies)
        → lead_qualified (ready to commit)
          → Enrollment pitched directly
            → Slot booked, payment link sent
              → Confirmation + reminders sent
                → student_enrolled (ZIRO_CLIENT creates student record)
                  → Outcome recorded
                    → Client report updated
```

At `student_enrolled`, ZiroWork's active work ends.

