## What AI Can't Touch

AI handles new enrollment conversations only.

| Situation | Action |
|---|---|
| New inquiry | AI handles — qualify and enroll |
| Rescheduling inside enrollment flow | AI handles |
| Pricing question (approved answer on file) | AI handles |
| Pricing question (no approved answer) | Escalate |
| Billing dispute or refund | Escalate immediately |
| Angry parent or complaint | Escalate immediately |
| Current student changing their schedule | Escalate |
| Cancellation | Escalate |
| Unclear intent | One clarifying question, then escalate |

Every escalation is logged with severity, reason, and open/resolved status. Zach resolves manually.

