## What to Reject

| Reject | Why |
|---|---|
| Full CRM replacement as the first sale | Too much trust required before value is proven |
| Trial as the default close | Enrolled is the goal. Trial is a fallback. |
| Generic AI for all service businesses | Weak positioning. Music school authority is the edge. |
| Deep calendar dependency day one | Creates a blocker. Start with protected slots. |
| Taking custody of school funds early | Trust and compliance risk. Use their payment links. |
| Teacher management, payroll, lesson notes | Phase 4 work. Don't build it before Phase 1 is proven. |
| Feature usage as the main score | Booked enrollments and revenue recovered matter. Features don't. |

