## Build Sequence

Build in trust-earning order.

| Phase | Focus | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| 1. Enrollment | Fast response, qualify, direct enrollment, protected slots, reminders | ZiroWork can create enrolled students |
| 2. Recovery | Old lead reactivation, no-show recovery, post-trial follow-up | ZiroWork can recover missed revenue |
| 3. Integrations | Calendar read-only, payment status, email, SMS sync | Trust and usage justify deeper access |
| 4. Operations | Retention, teacher utilization, source attribution, SSOT | ZiroWork is trusted infrastructure |

Do not build Phase 4 before Phase 1 works.

